    <title>Improve Community 2024 feed to append "and X other people" to "mentioned you"</title>
    <updated>2024-12-13T14:41:01.761000+01:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Sandra_Rossi</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/145194</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;In my Notification feed, I receive messages like this:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Sandra_Rossi_0-1734096572318.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/201260iBA01E9A6F3A780C6/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Sandra_Rossi_0-1734096572318.png" alt="Sandra_Rossi_0-1734096572318.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;In fact, the message targets a bunch of people, so it's not really a message targeting me specifically:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Sandra_Rossi_1-1734096716808.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/201262i307C0E1CEF58AC37/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Sandra_Rossi_1-1734096716808.png" alt="Sandra_Rossi_1-1734096716808.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Is it possible to change the message "@mentioned you in" to "&lt;STRONG&gt;@mentioned you and 11 other people in&lt;/STRONG&gt;"?&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Thank you.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Sandra&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/questions-about-sap-websites/improve-community-2024-feed-to-append-quot-and-x-other-people-quot-to-quot/qaq-p/13962902"/>
    <published>2024-12-13T14:41:01.761000+01:00</published>
  </entry>
