  <entry>
    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/questions-about-sap-websites/random-p-user-selected-during-login-to-community-2024-i-can-t-choose/qaq-p/13977538</id>
    <title>Random P-User selected during login to Community 2024 (I can't choose)</title>
    <updated>2025-01-06T11:02:13.971000+01:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Sandra_Rossi</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/145194</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;Hello,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;This is an email I have just sent to&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="mailto:sso@sap.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;sso@sap.com&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;and &lt;A href="mailto:community@sap.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;community@sap.com&lt;/A&gt;. I post it in Community 2024 in case other people have the same issue.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;When I log in to &lt;A href="https://community.sap.com/t5/notificationfeed/page" target="_blank"&gt;Notification feed - SAP Community&lt;/A&gt; every morning under my SAP Universal ID (primary email address: xxxxxxxxxxxxx@gmail.com), there’s no popup asking me under which account I want to login, it defaults to a linked P-User that I hadn’t use for days or months, it doesn’t select the last user I have used (S-User).&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;If I then go to &lt;A href="https://me.sap.com/servicessupport/knowledge" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;Services &amp;amp; Support - SAP for Me&lt;/A&gt;, of course there’s an issue because the current account is a P-User instead of a S-User, so I have to log out and log in to &lt;A href="https://me.sap.com/servicessupport/knowledge" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;Services &amp;amp; Support - SAP for Me&lt;/A&gt;, there’s a popup from which I can select my S-User.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;If I log out, restart Edge, log in to &lt;A href="https://community.sap.com/t5/notificationfeed/page" target="_blank"&gt;Notification feed - SAP Community&lt;/A&gt; again, my P-User is selected again by default, instead of selecting the last used account (the S-user).&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;For information, the popup is also shown if I log in to &lt;A href="https://developers.sap.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;SAP Developer Center | Official Resources for SAP Developers&lt;/A&gt;.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Is it possible to either select by default the last used account or let the user choose any of the linked accounts?&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Workaround: I could unlink all my P-Users from my SAP Universal ID/secondary email address xxxxxxxxxxx@mycompany.com, but it’s the worst solution of course.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Steps to reproduce:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;OL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Start Edge&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Start inPrivate window&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Login to &lt;A href="https://community.sap.com/t5/notificationfeed/page" target="_blank"&gt;https://community.sap.com/t5/notificationfeed/page&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Use of my SAP Universal ID primary email address: xxxxxxxxxxxx@gmail.com&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;.&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;Click Next.&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Sandra_Rossi_0-1736156804448.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/208060iE31F3CC41C7840F6/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Sandra_Rossi_0-1736156804448.png" alt="Sandra_Rossi_0-1736156804448.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Type the password.&lt;BR /&gt;Click Sign in.&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Sandra_Rossi_6-1736157182110.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/208069iD9FBD4A322836403/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Sandra_Rossi_6-1736157182110.png" alt="Sandra_Rossi_6-1736157182110.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;PROBLEM: I cannot select which linked account I want to use; the Community page is shown, which means that one account was automatically selected (I don’t know which one).&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Sandra_Rossi_2-1736156911459.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/208063iFAA5E4E21D31106A/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Sandra_Rossi_2-1736156911459.png" alt="Sandra_Rossi_2-1736156911459.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Login to &lt;A href="https://me.sap.com/servicessupport/knowledge" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;https://me.sap.com/servicessupport/knowledge&lt;/A&gt;.&lt;BR /&gt;PROBLEM: weird message “Due to inactivity…” Click “click here”.&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Sandra_Rossi_3-1736156940860.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/208064i0F23903617F6DDC6/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Sandra_Rossi_3-1736156940860.png" alt="Sandra_Rossi_3-1736156940860.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;PROBLEM: click the user settings, you can see that a random P-User account was selected by the Community login.&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Sandra_Rossi_4-1736156996612.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/208065i9501F8FAD44D2E43/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Sandra_Rossi_4-1736156996612.png" alt="Sandra_Rossi_4-1736156996612.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;For information, here are my linked accounts (&lt;A href="https://account.sap.com/manage/accounts" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;SAP Universal ID Account Manager&lt;/A&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":disappointed_face:"&gt;😞&lt;/span&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Sandra_Rossi_5-1736157105380.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/208067iE3F9231B0AA72A87/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Sandra_Rossi_5-1736157105380.png" alt="Sandra_Rossi_5-1736157105380.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/OL&gt;&lt;P&gt;For comparison, I don’t have any issue if I first login via Services &amp;amp; Support - SAP for Me, I can select my account:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;OL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Start Edge&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Start inPrivate window&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Login to &lt;A href="https://me.sap.com/servicessupport/knowledge" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;https://me.sap.com/servicessupport/knowledge&lt;/A&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Use of my SAP Universal ID primary email address: xxxxxxxxxxx@gmail.com&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;.&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;Click Next.&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Sandra_Rossi_7-1736157435166.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/208070iBC029C4304C41E35/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Sandra_Rossi_7-1736157435166.png" alt="Sandra_Rossi_7-1736157435166.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Type the password.&lt;BR /&gt;Click Sign in.&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Sandra_Rossi_6-1736157182110.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/208069iD9FBD4A322836403/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Sandra_Rossi_6-1736157182110.png" alt="Sandra_Rossi_6-1736157182110.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;GOOD, I can select the account I want:&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Sandra_Rossi_8-1736157519393.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/208072i2140A3ED08A5EE35/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Sandra_Rossi_8-1736157519393.png" alt="Sandra_Rossi_8-1736157519393.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia